pensacola is reviewing the courtmartial recommendations hessler 
said 
torchia earlier rejected an option for nonjudicial punishment 
but the four instructors accepted the offer 
a courtmartial offers a chance for acquittal but a conviction 
results in more serious penalties than those arising from 
nonjudicial hearings 
