to assess his 3yearold reform program and set a course for the 
future gorbachev recalled that previous attempts in the 1950s and 
1960s to reform the soviet economy all were swallowed up by the 
system 
in an impassioned 40minute speech broadcast later on national 
television gorbachev told the 5000 delegates assembled in the 
