18 approved 3287 million in contracts for the railmobile mx a 
missile he says is necessary to counter two mobile missiles already 
deployed by the soviets the 10warhead ss24 based on rails and 
the singlewarhead ss25 on trucks 
the mx can carry 10 warheads and air force officials call in 
the most accurate strategic missile in the us arsenal 
we are not terminating the program hoffman told reporters 
at a briefing we are moving ahead on a plan that we have laid 
out 
we live in hope that if not this year then next year the 
congress will see the wisdom of the approach that we have been 
