those who make it big in either place from ronald reagan and 
tax rebel howard jarvis to mario cuomo and real estate mogul donald 
trump usually end up as familiar figures in the rest of the 
united states 
in economic terms california is riding the crest of a boom as 
americas gateway to the thriving pacific rim new york which grew 
to dominance as americas chief portofentry from europe is 
enjoying an upswing itself 
but the empire state is also struggling to phase out its 
decaying manufacturing industries and replace them with the kind of 
hightechnology and defenseoriented companies that have become a 
mainstay of californias economy 
